## 18) High‑Yield Formula Clusters (Memorize as Groups)

### Motion & Gravity
- v = u + at; s = ut + ½at²; v² = u² + 2as.
- v (orbital) = √(GM/R); ve = √(2GM/R); T² ∝ r³.

